descriptionHtml:
I am always amazed about the characters of other people and how well they turn out. And then I'm kinda disappointed that those characters aren't shared. My latest character seems to have turned out pretty well, and I have a lot of fun playing this aesthetic setup. So this is why I wanted to share this preset with you guys.

She is supposed to be a Nord, but you might be able to use the preset with any humanoid race (I didn't test it though). 

You will probably need [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800/]Groovtamas XPMS Extended[/url] for all sliders to work properly.

To install, drop the file into:
"Data\skse\plugins\CharGen\Presets"
and load the preset in the race menu
